  "title": "Cyclist Patrol",
  "description": "<p><strong>Get PAID to RIDE! Join Us as a Full-Time Cyclist Patrol Officer</strong></p>\n<p>Love being outdoors and staying active? We’re looking for energetic and responsible individuals to join our team and yes, you’ll literally <strong>get paid to ride bicycles around the city</strong>!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Your mission:</strong> help keep our shared bikes in top condition, ensure proper parking, and make every ride smooth and enjoyable for our users.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What Does a Cyclist Patrol Officer Do?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Patrol assigned areas to check bike conditions and parking compliance</li>\n  <li>Report damaged or missing bikes through our system</li>\n  <li>Submit simple daily reports via app</li>\n  <li>Handle ad-hoc tasks assigned by the Operations Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Cyclist Patrol Officer Superpowers</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Singapore’s geography</li>\n  <li>Able to walk or cycle for extended periods</li>\n  <li>Responsible, observant, and proactive</li>\n  <li>Comfortable using smartphones and basic apps</li>\n  <li>Experience in fieldwork or outdoor tasks is an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You’ll Love This Role</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Get paid to ride</strong> — stay active, fit, and healthy while earning</li>\n  <li>Flexible, outdoor work environment</li>\n  <li>Be part of a growing movement promoting cleaner, greener transport in the city</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>\n<p>Pay: $2,800.00 - $2,860.00 per month</p>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Flexible schedule</li>\n  <li>Professional development</li>\n  <li>Promotion to permanent employee</li>\n</ul>",
